properties.Name: PartyContract

Columns.Name: PartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.

Columns.Name: ContractId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Contract.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period start timestamp that the information is valid or effective as of.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period end timestamp that the information is valid or effective as of.

Columns.Name: PartyContractNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the party contract.

Properties.Description:
The one or more Contracts specifying the terms, conditions  and obligations binding the party to another party.

Note:
One or more parties may be party to a contract, which is why PARTY is part of the key.
